{"title":"Oracle中date错误，ORA-01830: date format picture ends before converting entire input string","date":"2018-09-28T18:26:00.000Z","link":"post/266","categories":["DataBase"],"updated":"2019-04-27T12:44:13.631Z","content":"<p><img src=\"http://pqiuhq1tw.bkt.clouddn.com/2252438278.png\" alt class=\"article-img\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"错误原因：\">错误原因：<a href=\"post/266#错误原因：\"></a></h3><p><img src=\"http://pqiuhq1tw.bkt.clouddn.com/222729823.png\" alt><br><strong>错误产生原因:date类型不能包含秒以后的精度</strong></p>\n<h3 id=\"解决方法\">解决方法<a href=\"post/266#解决方法\"></a></h3><p><strong>删除秒精度后面的数字即可</strong></p>\n","prev":{"title":"关于Java中length、length()、size()的区别","link":"post/268"},"next":{"title":"Git解决冲突","link":"post/263"},"plink":"https://1056438464.github.io/post/266/"}